OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1780646725
OL,3,CCare of triple killer was
OL,4,C'unacceptably poor' says minister in
OL,5,Capology, inquiry
OL,7,FThe care of paranoid schizophrenic
OL,8,FValdo Calocane before he killed three
OL,9,Fpeople was "unacceptably poor", a
OL,10,Fminister has told an inquiry.
OL,12,FBaroness Gillian Merron, minister for
OL,13,Fmental health, apologised to the
OL,14,Fsurvivors of the attacks for a
OL,15,F"serious omission" by the Government,
OL,16,Fwhich did not consult them before the
OL,17,Finquiry was announced last year.
OL,26,@qD@LOUqD@^O]wD@AOUwD@RO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1780646725
OL,3,CCare of triple killer was
OL,4,C'unacceptably poor' says minister in
OL,5,Capology, inquiry
OL,7,FCalocane fatally stabbed students
OL,8,FBarnaby Webber and Grace O'Malley-
OL,9,FKumar, both 19, and grandfather Ian
OL,10,FCoates, 65, before trying to murder
OL,11,Fthree more people with a van on June
OL,12,F13 2023, in Nottingham, leaving them
OL,13,Fseriously injured.
OL,15,FCalocane was detained under mental
OL,16,Fhealth laws four times while under the
OL,17,Fcare of Nottinghamshire Healthcare NHS
OL,18,FFoundation Trust (NHFT) until he was
OL,19,Fdischarged in 2022.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1780646725
OL,3,CCare of triple killer was
OL,4,C'unacceptably poor' says minister in
OL,5,Capology, inquiry
OL,7,FOn Thursday, counsel to the inquiry,
OL,8,FRachel Langdale KC, read part of
OL,9,FBaroness Merron's witness statement,
OL,10,Fwhich said, "The department
OL,11,F(Department of Health and Social Care)
OL,12,Frecognises there were failures in
OL,13,Fprovision of care to VC (Valdo
OL,14,FCalocane), particularly the lack of
OL,15,Foversight of his mental health, the
OL,16,Fyear before the attacks.
OL,18,F"Unacceptably poor, should not have
OL,19,Fbeen allowed to happen."
OL,26,@rD@MOUzD@AOU{D@XO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1780646725
OL,3,CCare of triple killer was
OL,4,C'unacceptably poor' says minister in
OL,5,Capology, inquiry
OL,7,FThe statement continued, "NHFT
OL,8,Foperates within a broader national
OL,9,Fframework, and it's certainly not the
OL,10,Fdepartment's position that
OL,11,FNottinghamshire Healthcare Foundation
OL,12,FTrust is solely to blame for the
OL,13,Ffailings in VC's care."
OL,15,FMs Langdale asked, "Where would you
OL,16,Fwiden that then? Are you saying a
OL,17,FGovernment or Department of Health
OL,18,Fresponsibility too ` the failings in
OL,19,Fhis care?"
OL,26,@oD@ZOUuD@WO]wD@TOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1780646725
OL,3,CCare of triple killer was
OL,4,C'unacceptably poor' says minister in
OL,5,Capology, inquiry
OL,7,FThe minister replied: "The matter of
OL,8,Ffailings in the care of an individual,
OL,9,Fof course, can sit in many places. The
OL,10,Fintent of that paragraph is not to
OL,11,Fpass on responsibility but to take
OL,12,Fresponsibility.
OL,14,F"It is the very reason that one of our
OL,15,Ffirst acts in terms of the King's
OL,16,FSpeech... was to include the Mental
OL,17,FHealth Bill which has now become the
OL,18,FMental Health Act, because we
OL,19,Frecognise that this was an outdated
OL,20,Fframework.
OL,26,@oD@WOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1780646725
OL,3,CCare of triple killer was
OL,4,C'unacceptably poor' says minister in
OL,5,Capology, inquiry
OL,7,F"The provisions of it remain sound,
OL,8,Fbut what we have done is modernise
OL,9,Fthat framework on the basis of
OL,10,Fexperience.
OL,12,F"And I should say... some of the
OL,13,Fexperiences of previous inquiries too,
OL,14,Fand the experience of the events of
OL,15,Fthis inquiry, as we have heard
OL,16,Fdirectly from those affected."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUxD@^O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1780646725
OL,3,CCare of triple killer was
OL,4,C'unacceptably poor' says minister in
OL,5,Capology, inquiry
OL,7,FAddressing the bereaved families at
OL,8,Fthe start of her evidence, Baroness
OL,9,FMerron said: "I want to express my
OL,10,Fgratitude but my absolute respect for
OL,11,Fthe way in which you have engaged with
OL,12,Fus, despite what I can only describe
OL,13,Fperhaps as unimaginable pain, so I
OL,14,Fthank you and deeply respect you for
OL,15,Fthat."
OL,26,@qD@NOUwD@FO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1780646725
OL,3,CCare of triple killer was
OL,4,C'unacceptably poor' says minister in
OL,5,Capology, inquiry
OL,7,FSophie Cartwright KC, who represents
OL,8,FWayne Birkett and Sharon Miller, two
OL,9,Fsurvivors of Calocane's attacks, said
OL,10,Fthere had been "no consultation,
OL,11,Fcontact or engagement with any of the
OL,12,Fsurviving victims" before the inquiry
OL,13,Fwas announced.
OL,15,FBaroness Merron replied, "I
OL,16,Finterrogated on this point before
OL,17,Fcoming to the inquiry and I believe
OL,18,Fthat situation that you outline is
OL,19,Fcorrect.
OL,26,@rD@POUtD@RO]wD@ZOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1780646725
OL,3,CCare of triple killer was
OL,4,C'unacceptably poor' says minister in
OL,5,Capology, inquiry
OL,7,F"What I would like to say is, with the
OL,8,Fbenefit of hindsight, that wasn't the
OL,9,Fright way to proceed.
OL,11,F"The Secretary of State, when he did
OL,12,Freceive contact from the survivors,
OL,13,Fdid meet with the survivors. But I do
OL,14,Ftake on board the implied criticism,
OL,15,For perhaps the actual criticism, that
OL,16,Fsurvivors were not included as they
OL,17,Fshould have been.
OL,19,F"I accept that and wish to apologise
OL,20,Ffor that."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOU{D@AOU|D@JO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1780646725
OL,3,CCare of triple killer was
OL,4,C'unacceptably poor' says minister in
OL,5,Capology, inquiry
OL,7,FShe added, "I'm sure it has caused
OL,8,Fgreat distress and, as I say, if we
OL,9,Fcould possibly rerun it ` and we
OL,10,Fcannot ` but if we could I know we
OL,11,Fwould do it differently."
OL,13,FMs Langdale said, "What I'm going to
OL,14,Fsuggest is it was a serious omission
OL,15,Fbecause, as victims of this attack,
OL,16,Fthey should have been consulted prior
OL,17,Fto the inquiry being announced."
OL,19,FBaroness Merron replied, "I'm
OL,20,Faccepting that and I'm apologising for
OL,21,Fthat."
OL,26,@oD@LOUsD@YO]uD@SOUyD@`O]{D@ZOU}D@FO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/11
